WEBVTT

00:00:30.476 --> 00:00:32.553
Now, there he is calling to his friends.

00:00:32.577 --> 00:00:34.577
Now, if you notice that the first follower

00:00:34.601 --> 00:00:37.976
is actually an underestimated form
of leadership in itself.

00:00:38.000 --> 00:00:39.976
It takes guts to stand out like that.

00:00:40.484 --> 00:00:44.976
The first follower is what transforms
a lone nut into a leader.

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:46.976
(Laughter)

00:00:47.000 --> 00:00:50.221
(Applause)

00:00:50.245 --> 00:00:51.976
And here comes a second follower.

00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:54.398
Now it's not a lone nut,
it's not two nuts --

00:00:54.422 --> 00:00:56.976
three is a crowd, and a crowd is news.

00:00:57.000 --> 00:00:58.976
So a movement must be public.

00:00:59.343 --> 00:01:02.576
It's important to show
not just the leader, but the followers,